     C           P2TKR     CAT  L7TKR2:0  P2TKR
     C           P2TKR     CAT  '-':0     P2TKR
     C           P2TKR     CAT  L7TKR3:0  P2TKR
     C           P2TKR     CAT  '-':0     P2TKR
